  "title": "Coordinates HUD",
  "description": "An advanced Minecraft coordinate display mod that provides a customizable HUD showing coordinates, biome information, and much more!",
  "body": "<h1><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Minecraft-1.21.5-green\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Java-21-orange\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Fabric-✓-blue\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Forge-✓-red\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/NeoForge-✓-orange\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Quilt-✓-purple\"></h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/quillphen\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Support me-Patreon-ff424d?logo=patreon&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Patreon\"></a> &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/8GydmUN3xq\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Join our Discord-5865F2?logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/quillphen\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Support me-Ko--fi-571db5?logo=kofi&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Support me on Ko-fi\"></p></h1></p>\n<h1 style=\"font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 32px; color: #ddd;\">Coordinates HUD</h1>\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #bbb;\"><strong>Coordinates HUD</strong> is a clean and highly customizable HUD for Minecraft. It displays essential data like coordinates, biome, direction, and more &mdash; without clutter. Perfect for explorers, builders, and technical players alike.</p>\n<h2 style=\"font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 22px; color: #ccc;\">Theme Previews</h2>\n<div style=\"border: 1px solid #333;\"><img style=\"margin-right: 10px;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1220/32/screenshot-2025-06-14-181612-png.png\" height=\"180\"> <img style=\"margin-right: 10px;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1220/33/screenshot-2025-06-14-181540-png.png\" height=\"180\"> <img style=\"margin-right: 10px;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1220/34/screenshot-2025-06-14-181523-png.png\" height=\"180\"> <img style=\"margin-right: 10px;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1220/38/screenshot-2025-06-14-181628-png.png\" height=\"180\"> <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1220/36/screenshot-2025-06-14-181440-png.png\" height=\"180\"></div>\n<h2 style=\"font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 22px; color: #ccc;\">Compass</h2>\n<p><img style=\"border: 1px solid #444;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1220/37/screenshot-2025-06-14-181406-png.png\" width=\"127\" height=\"137\"></p>\n<h2>Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Real-time XYZ coordinates</li>\n<li>Biome and dimension display</li>\n<li>Cardinal direction compass</li>\n<li>Real-world &amp; in-game clocks</li>\n<li>Weather, light levels, slime chunk check</li>\n<li>Speed, FPS, chunk and motion tracking</li>\n<li>Health, hunger, armor, target block info</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Customization</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Built-in themes: Default, Dark, Rainbow, Minimal</li>\n<li>Custom colors and background options</li>\n<li>Adjustable position and scale</li>\n<li>Smooth animations, toggleable sections</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Keybinds</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>C</strong>: Toggle HUD</li>\n<li><strong>G</strong>: Toggle Compass</li>\n<li><strong>H</strong>: Open Config Menu</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Configuration Interface:</p>\n<p><img style=\"border: 1px solid #444;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1220/35/screenshot-2025-06-14-181504-png.png\" width=\"349\" height=\"347\"></p>\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Download for Fabric, Forge, NeoForge, or Quilt</li>\n<li>Place the <code>.jar</code> file into your <code>mods</code> folder</li>\n<li>Launch Minecraft &mdash; it auto-loads!</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Requirements</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Minecraft 1.21.5</li>\n<li>Java 21 or higher</li>\n<li>Fabric Loader 0.15.11+ with Fabric API</li>\n<li>Forge 52.0.17+</li>\n<li>NeoForge 21.1.42+</li>\n<li>Quilt Loader (fully compatible)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Support &amp; Source</h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Report bugs, request features, or view the code on <a style=\"color: #3598db;\" href=\"https://github.com/Hiba550/CoordHUD\" rel=\"nofollow\">GitHub</a>.</p>",
